               <msContents>
                  <summary>
                     <p>I) ልፋፈ፡ጽድቅ“Bandlet of Righteousness” (pp. <locus target="#1"/>-<locus target="#31"/>
                        <locus from="36" to="40"/>) </p>
                     <p>II) ) ጸሎተ፡ መንገደ፡ሰማይ“Prayer of the Journey to Heaven” (pp. <locus from="40" to="54"/>)</p>
                     <p>III) ዜና፡ሕማማቲሁ፡ለመድኃኔ፡ዓለም“Story of the Sufferings of the Savior of the World”, revealed to Mary Magdalen, Salome and Elizabeth (pp. <locus from="55" to="62"/>), a version of the apocryphal “Story of the Passions of Christ”, see Piovanelli <locus target="#2014"/>esp. p. <locus target="#613"/>and footnote <locus target="#18"/>; Piovanelli <locus target="#2015"/>.</p>
                     
                     
                     
                  </summary>
                
               </msContents>
